604
00:36:38,000 --> 00:36:39,960
No era mi intención mantenerme alejado.

605
00:36:41,599 --> 00:36:43,079
Me enfadé porque supieras sobre

606
00:36:43,079 --> 00:36:44,840
El comportamiento escandaloso de Chen Xuanqing

607
00:36:45,880 --> 00:36:46,320
pero,

608
00:36:49,679 --> 00:36:51,000
pero no me lo dijo.

609
00:36:52,199 --> 00:36:53,400
¿Te lo digo?

610
00:36:54,480 --> 00:36:55,480
Dígame usted.

611
00:36:56,000 --> 00:36:57,159
Qué harías

612
00:36:57,400 --> 00:36:58,400
¿Y si estuvieras en mi lugar?

613
00:37:01,320 --> 00:37:03,119
Dilo sin rodeos.

614
00:37:04,159 --> 00:37:05,719
Dile a ti y a Chen Xuanqing

615
00:37:06,880 --> 00:37:08,280
