706
00:41:46,679 --> 00:41:47,519
No.

707
00:41:48,519 --> 00:41:49,440
Es probable que lo sea.

708
00:41:49,920 --> 00:41:51,559
para interceder por Wang.

709
00:42:08,880 --> 00:42:10,239
Media pulgada más cerca y lo haría

710
00:42:10,400 --> 00:42:11,880
